      • buildAttrNameList

        public java.util.List buildAttrNameList(MigrationNode node)
        Builds a list of node attributes, according to the following: - Adds the node attributes (ordered alphabeticMPally) to the end of the static attribute list. - Node attributes are added according the the injectable inclusion/exclusion criteria - Attribute order will be preserved in the static list - Node attributes will be sorted alphabetically and appended to the end of the list - If a node attribute is specified in the static list, it will not be added again
